Package com.intellij.vcs.log

Interface VcsLogObjectsFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VcsLogObjectsFactoryImpl

    public interface VcsLogObjectsFactory
    Use this factory to create correct instances of such commonly used intellij.platform.vcs.log objects as Hash or VcsShortCommitDetails.
